meanings.definition: Unable to be named or identified.
meanings.sent1: The mysterious creature in the forest was truly unnameable.

meanings.sent3: The unnameable shadow in the corner turned out to be a playful kitten.
meanings.sent4: The unnameable beauty of the sunset left everyone in awe.
meanings.sent5: The unnameable scent of the flowers filled the room with a sweet fragrance.
